  Introduction                                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Tử Vi 2026: Coi Ngày & Lịch Âm ("we", "our", "the App") is a Vietnamese astrology (Tử Vi) application. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal  
  information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our App.                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Information We Collect                                                                                                                                                      

  Personal Information

  The App does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal information. All astrology data you enter (date of birth, gender, lunar/solar calendar preferences) is stored       
  locally on your device only and is never sent to our servers or any third party.
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Automatically Collected Information                                                                                                                                           
   
  The App uses Google AdMob to display advertisements. Through AdMob, the following information may be automatically collected:                                                 
  - Advertising ID (Google Advertising ID)                                                                                                                                    
  - Device information (device model, operating system version)                                                                                                                 
  - IP address                                                                                                                                                                
  - General location (country/region level, not precise location)                                                                                                               
  - Ad interaction data (views, clicks)                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                
  How We Use Information                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                
  - To provide personalized astrology readings based on your input                                                                                                              
  - To display relevant advertisements through Google AdMob                                                                                                                     
  - To improve the App's performance and user experience                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Third-Party Services                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                
  The App uses the following third-party service:                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                              
  - Google AdMob — for serving advertisements. Google's privacy policy applies to data collected through AdMob. You can review Google's Privacy Policy at                       
  https://policies.google.com/privacy                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Data Storage                                                                                                                                                                  
   
  All user-entered data is stored locally on your device using an internal database. We do not operate any external servers to collect or store your data. If you uninstall the 
  App, all locally stored data will be permanently deleted.                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                
  Children's Privacy                                                                                                                                                            
   
  The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age. The App is intended for general audiences.                                       
                                                                                                                                                                              
  Your Rights                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                              
  Since all your data is stored locally on your device, you have full control over it. You can delete all data at any time by clearing the App's data in your device settings or
   by uninstalling the App.                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                
